he latter did not open the box immediately. 'Me too,' he said.

'Many times, many times. Good night, little girl.' Having hung up the receiver he sighed and opened the box. However, he turned in such a way that Luzhin could see nothing from behind his black shoulder.

Luzhin moved cautiously, but a cushion slid onto the floor and the gentleman quickly looked round. 'What are you doing here?' he asked, spying Luzhin in the dark corner. 'My, my, how bad it is to eavesdrop!'

Luzhin remained silent